{"4212640": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Naughty Nate : Tattoo", "steam_appid": 4212640, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>別忘了加入願望清單</strong> 💚🩵❤️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4212640/extras/f7f7bdf093d41a6a94ef9943546a64f0.avif?t=1771879249\" width=779 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>21歲的Nate在被前一份工作解雇後，開始在一家刺青店實習。當他接待第一批客人時，他的命運與三位截然不同的女性交織在一起——每一位都可能徹底改變他的生活。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Naughty Nate: Tattoo</strong> 結合誘惑性的敘事與選擇驅動的玩法。<br>每位女性都擁有獨特的個性、渴望與秘密——而<strong>你的選擇將塑造Nate的關係發展</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立信任、調情、冒險，或保持謹慎。<br>每個選擇都會影響場景、關係等級與故事結局。<br>做出明智決定，解鎖親密而熱情的時刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色 :</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4212640/extras/ca97f2aab09fe6ee3591cb9ee6b47b0d.avif?t=1771879249\" width=779 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nate堅強、哥德風的前任女友。冷漠、強勢且情感封閉。過去的火焰仍在暗處燃燒——而Gwen毫不猶豫地重新點燃它。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4212640/extras/cd82905e3f465e96021662f906999cd0.avif?t=1771879249\" width=779 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刺青店安靜害羞的常客。溫柔、容易害羞，但只要向Nate敞開心扉，就會展現出令人意外的深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4212640/extras/0a15bff3c205d46b960672123e7cbbad.avif?t=1771879249\" width=779 height=242 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精力充沛、自信、略帶瘋狂——以最迷人的方式展現。Lena喜歡混亂、樂趣與即興時刻，並將Nate吸入她火熱的軌道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色 : </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>三位獨特女性</strong>，各自擁有不同的個性與關係線</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>基於選擇的對話</strong>，決定關係的親密程度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>多重結局</strong>，依你的選擇而改變</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>性感、情感豐富且張力十足的互動</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>細膩的角色立繪與富表現力的場景</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個選擇都至關重要。<br>每個瞬間都可能讓你們更靠近……或失去一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入Nate的世界。<br><strong>追隨渴望，塑造你的故事。</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>別忘了加入願望清單</strong> 💚🩵❤️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4212640/extras/f7f7bdf093d41a6a94ef9943546a64f0.avif?t=1771879249\" width=779 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>21歲的Nate在被前一份工作解雇後，開始在一家刺青店實習。當他接待第一批客人時，他的命運與三位截然不同的女性交織在一起——每一位都可能徹底改變他的生活。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Naughty Nate: Tattoo</strong> 結合誘惑性的敘事與選擇驅動的玩法。<br>每位女性都擁有獨特的個性、渴望與秘密——而<strong>你的選擇將塑造Nate的關係發展</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立信任、調情、冒險，或保持謹慎。<br>每個選擇都會影響場景、關係等級與故事結局。<br>做出明智決定，解鎖親密而熱情的時刻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色 :</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4212640/extras/